Package: annolite
Type: Package
Title: Lightweight Fulltext Display and Annotation Tools
Version: 0.0.1.9002
Date: 2020-11-04
Authors@R: person("Andreas", "Blaette", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "andreas.blaette@uni-due.de")
Description: The package includes an htmlwidget 'fulltext' and a shiny gadget to inspect the fulltext of (sub-)corpora, and for coding and adding free-text memos. 
